See README.tau for general instructions.  This README contains specific
instructions for Cori KNL.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Load modules, set up dynamic linking:
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

module swap PrgEnv-intel PrgEnv-gnu
module swap craype-haswell craype-mic-knl
module load cmake/3.11.4
export CRAYPE_LINK_TYPE=dynamic

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Build tau with:
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

./configure -mpi -pthread -bfd=download -arch=craycnl
make install

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Build ADIOS2 with:
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

cmake -DCMAKE_C_COMPILER=`which cc` -DCMAKE_CXX_COMPILER=`which CC` \
-DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=`pwd` -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug ../ADIOS2
make -j8

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Run heat transfer example ADIOS2 with:
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

see job.slurm.cori for details.



